                                PortageLive
                        Virtual Application creation

This directory contains the virtual appliance creation instructions, with
samples for the three scripts you can manually cut-and-paste into the VMWare
Studio interface, if you chose to use VMWare Studio.

Please read the "PortageLive Manual" section of the Portage 1.4.1 User Manual
first!
